{"tid":1323902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果記者唔該入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-16T11:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T13:58:18.000Z","uid":257516,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d96203cd7f1d8f644af33241a4e019a74fc44b66","tid":1323902,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:46:57.000Z","msg":"記者朋友 巴絲們大家好<br />\n唔知大家有無印象早幾年有個網站可以俾公眾查閱議員投票紀錄？<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.legcovotes.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legcovotes.net&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=81cc3ce7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.legcovotes.net</a><br />\n裡面有晒所有議員嘅投票紀錄 介面清晰 非常User Friendly!<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/1f8d16ede1abe9e286e29c947fd220b2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F1f8d16ede1abe9e286e29c947fd220b2.png&h=a1389643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/567f61f4251c4c9d9ed8f97a700eef29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F567f61f4251c4c9d9ed8f97a700eef29.png&h=c5cf041d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/a33856618a3ac0c88a28c38d141bef0b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2Fa33856618a3ac0c88a28c38d141bef0b.png&h=65825671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/b107556a5a4fff61f4b62edeb2175474.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2Fb107556a5a4fff61f4b62edeb2175474.png&h=f5377733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但呢個網站自從第五屆立法會會期(2012-2016)完咗之後就冇再Update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家普羅大眾要睇議員投票紀錄就只可以上立法會個網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話check唔到 不過冇電腦就唔使旨意極速check到紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/counmtg/yr16-20/mtg_1617.htm#cm20161012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fyr16-20%2Fmtg_1617.htm%23cm20161012&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=e43bb1ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/counmtg/yr16-20/mtg_1617.htm#cm20161012</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/6146c1e68ebc7dadde01c54eebf993ce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F6146c1e68ebc7dadde01c54eebf993ce.png&h=a15ebc4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/74b1a0b5650d7614cece89d18b6af157.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F74b1a0b5650d7614cece89d18b6af157.png&h=2c8652d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你 啲字細到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n梁國雄議員.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再講 個介面真係古老石山<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果蘋果可以做埋議員投票紀錄，暫時諗到好處有二<br />\n1. 方便市民監察議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家好多市民／選民根本唔會逐個逐個會議上Legco個網睇 根本正常人係無可能有咁多時間喺度keep住開pdf mon住啲議員<br />\n2. 做大個餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人話：其實依家蘋果收錢只會令到讀者光譜縮窄。但如果蘋果可以做埋呢一範，相信有唔少中立／藍絲願意課金睇蘋果<br />\n<br />\n另外 可以參考英國They Work For You<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theyworkforyou.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theyworkforyou.com%2F&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=3baa9e1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theyworkforyou.com/</a><br />\n對該議員有一個投票取態概覽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/e6bf24a840ef71bf8da949cbe86e17ce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2Fe6bf24a840ef71bf8da949cbe86e17ce.png&h=791dc60b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據議題分門別類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/b4c35852aefe388e8a0a3ef454094996.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2Fb4c35852aefe388e8a0a3ef454094996.png&h=f04da214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n按照日期排序<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/998daae5cc329bd4229ceda8c61bc5e3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F998daae5cc329bd4229ceda8c61bc5e3.png&h=bd582fbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb99b217b3180633200f6d8f2eef2f1521e5229d","tid":1323902,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:47:40.000Z","msg":"推到記者朋友入嚟"},{"pid":"7d0c864fe514e90a7485ea95e04df97da47d5008","tid":1323902,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:47:50.000Z","msg":"推到記者朋友入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad07e68033f27ed16abca13b07040e2d472262b0","tid":1323902,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:48:00.000Z","msg":"推到記者朋友入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c149552f03b64e353f7db323de4e57b15edbe7","tid":1323902,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:48:49.000Z","msg":"推到記者朋友入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmo