k\">https://lih.kg/1324088</a>"},{"pid":"97cd03f25081a648a816d688a8abacd2b0559c44","tid":1323902,"uid":158235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a1aad2dfc95271391540654d3ce95141941181d1","tid":1323902,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:14:19.000Z","msg":"又幾方便"},{"pid":"6c11362d3cd4f4381323b3f596947297b39c79a2","tid":1323902,"uid":50922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:58:18.000Z","msg":"蘋果點會搞呀, 泛民太多出賣香港人嘅投票記錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其係民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}